{"tid":1801982,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係時候要擁有屬於自己嘅國旗","createTime":"2019-12-29T05:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T11:00:30.000Z","uid":324752,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9ea67c3988284ca78656d1354af43158f7704f","tid":1801982,"uid":324752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:41:06.000Z","msg":"抗爭左半年，我哋香港人前所無比咁團結，連國歌都作埋出嚟，但係，我哋依然係揮緊光復旗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋缺乏一支有代表性圖像嘅國旗</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DWYRZ3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWYRZ3E.jpg&h=20a5df7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面嘅呢支旗喺由Dgxmusic片段中的圖像修改而成，個人應為暫時最適合作為香港嘅國旗，除咗<span style=\"color: orange;\">具代表性，簡樸，潔淨同美觀</span>之外，仲有幾個原因：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 象徵嘅核心價值</span></span><br />\n國旗嘅藍色代表着<span style=\"color: blue;\">民主</span>，而上下兩邊嘅白色則代表着自由，呢兩樣係我哋香港人一直爭取嘅普世價值，而自由中間夾住民主，代表先有自由，其後才有真正嘅民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（否則就好似中國啲小粉紅咁）<br />\n<br />\n而當中嘅18粒星星則代表住喺<span style=\"color: gold;\">18個區議會</span>嘅全港市民，一粒粒星星站在白色上。代表着我哋每個人都嚮往生活在自由嘅土地上，並上下一心，一同時刻致力維護中間藍色嘅民主制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.地理位置</span></span><br />\n國旗嘅顏色其實亦代表着香港嘅地理結構，雙方的白色代表着<span style=\"color: green;\">九龍和新界區</span>，而下方的白色代表着<span style=\"color: green;\">香港島</span>；中間嘅藍色則代表分隔兩地嘅<span style=\"color: blue;\">維多利亞港</span>，能夠充分體現香港嘅地形同既有風貌<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家認唔認同，但我第一眼睇到嘅時候就已經有呢個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祈求民主與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人  起義</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1b18a6dd257af5854ea26a55fb872b9ecaf6d4","tid":1801982,"uid":324752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"國旗真係好重要 睇吓人哋加塞同西藏，一個圖案佢有非常大嘅象徵意義"},{"pid":"cfa134686eddc62900a833f8a1ba86fe7a94c223","tid":1801982,"uid":156592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"7bef794fe73f0f9067a61041f0ac65f3edf590c4","tid":1801982,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"有集會啊 大家記得要去啊 熱門一個Po都冇 完全唔夠宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主可唔可以暫時頂置呢段嘢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AsKRfJJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsKRfJJ.jpg&h=c00de685&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"104e5ab317ebec414bba3d990ba3d74a72ce6cc4","tid":1801982,"uid":324752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"之前睇過咁多個國旗post, 真係覺得呢個非常適合同埋最有機會"},{"pid":"1457fe5624144eb8bc92ea18dff3a347a9a4e793","tid":1801982,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29dedc010abcae47dd2a7435e80ddc941bc627ef","tid":1801982,"uid":324752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔知大家認唔認同 國旗嘅重要性"},{"pid":"896598b4bd64a4b3943c46e326a08e2a56660a10","tid":1801982,"uid":324752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:44:12.000Z","msg":"Push +1"},{"pid":"5df